Interface DynamicGraph<E>

All Superinterfaces:
Graph
All Known Implementing Classes:
MyGraph
public interface DynamicGraph<E> extends Graph
DynamicGraph base class for graphs. A graph is a set of vertices and a set of edges. Vertices are represented by integers from 0 to n - 1. Edges are ordered pairs of vertices.
